SUMMARY:Roadwork AM — PUSH day
DESCRIPTION:PUSH DAY workout (5-10 min):\nPush-ups x12 / Pike push-ups x8 / Chair or bed tricep dips x12 — 3 rounds.\nDaily 4: vitamins (with the car key) / water ~80oz = 3 bottles\, one per stop / the workout / 5-min stretch tonight. Brutal-day floor: 20 squats + 10 push-ups (still counts). Log it: https://thecubeographer.github.io/roadwork/
